trans-unit.source: Specifies the painting style applied to multiple <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> objects contained in a form.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o estilo de desenho aplicado a vários <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> objetos contidos num formulário.

trans-unit.source: The ToolStripManagerRenderMode is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager> class and sets the painting style for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> objects that have their <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: O ToolStripManagerRenderMode é utilizada pela <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager>classe e define o desenho de estilo para <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>objetos que tenham a respetiva <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade definida como <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager>

trans-unit.source: You cannot explicitly set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to Custom, however the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is returned Custom when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is set to an extension of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> class that is not <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.
trans-unit.target: Não é possível definir explicitamente o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>como Custom, no entanto, a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>é devolvido personalizada quando <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName>está definido como uma extensão da <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer>classe que é não <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer>ou <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer"></xref> other than <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Indica a utilização de um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer"> </xref> diferente de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"></xref> to paint.
trans-unit.target: Indica a utilização de um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"> </xref> a pintura.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"></xref> to paint.
